description: American Uranium Corporation (American Uranium) is an exploration-stage company engaged in the acquisition and exploration of mineral property interests in the United States. The Company has an option and LLC agreement with Strathmore Resources (US) Ltd. Pursuant to the agreement, the Company has an option to earn-in a 60% interest in Strathmore's Pinetree-Reno Creek uranium property. The Pinetree-Reno Creek Property is located in the central Powder River Basin, within the Pumpkin Buttes Uranium District, and encompasses approximately 16,000 acres. On March 9, 2009, the Company dissolved its wholly owned subsidiary, American Uranium Corporation.
